data_manufacturer = []
for row in data2['platform']:
    if row in ['dc', 'gen', 'sat'] : data_manufacturer.append('sega')
    elif row in ['wiiu','gc', 'snes', 'n64', 'nes', 'gb', '3ds', 'gba', 'ds', 'wii']:   data_manufacturer.append('nintendo')
    elif row in ['xone', 'xb','x360']: data_manufacturer.append('microsoft')
    elif row in ['psv', 'psp', 'ps4', 'ps', 'ps3', 'ps2']: data_manufacturer.append('sony')
    elif row in ['pc']:  data_manufacturer.append('  ()')
    else:  data_manufacturer.append('no_name')
data2['manufacturer'] = data_manufacturer

data_xone = data_actual_period.query('platform == "xone"').dropna(subset=['user_score'])
data_pc = data_actual_period.query('platform == "pc"').dropna(subset=['user_score'])

print('   Xbox One:', np.var(data_xone['user_score']))
print('   PC:', np.var(data_pc['user_score']))
alpha = 0.05 #   

results = st.ttest_ind(data_xone['user_score'], data_pc['user_score'],equal_var = False)

print('p-:', results.pvalue)

if (results.pvalue < alpha):
    print("C    Xbox One  PC  ")
else:
    print("    Xbox One  PC ")
